Stay in the loop with everything you need to know.
We are now going forward and looking at the local council elections ,with that in mind, we are putting a call out to all local members across the 12 wards. We would like to invite anyone to submit their interest in becoming a Reform UK councillor candidate for these elections. We need 1 per ward totalling 12 people. We need to gather as many people as possible and also to get the grassroots movement flowing. If you are interested please come to our Monthly meetings details of which will be on the home page of the next upcoming meet.
There is a website describing what it entails being a local councillor.
This is a full list of current councillors for the wards,
